<p>This guide fixes that. It covers SEO for small business from the ground up: keyword research, on-page optimization, local search, content strategy, link building, technical basics, and measuring ROI. No fluff. No jargon without explanation. Just the exact playbook a small business owner needs to start ranking.</p>
