<h3>How to Calculate SEO ROI</h3>
<p>The formula is simple:</p>
<p><strong>SEO ROI = (Revenue from Organic - SEO Cost) / SEO Cost x 100</strong></p>
<p>If you spend $500 per month on SEO and organic search generates $3,000 in new revenue, your ROI is 500%.</p>
<p>Track this monthly. Learn more about <a href="/blog/measure-content-marketing-roi/">measuring content marketing ROI</a> with attribution models that connect blog visits to actual sales.</p>
